# knowledge/intel/

Skills and routines write audit reports here:
- competitive-scout summaries (competitive-scout-<client>-<date>.md)
- substrate decay audits (context-decay-<date>.md)
- brief freshness reports (brief-freshness-<client>-<date>.md)
- quarterly recap drafts (durability-recap-<client>-<Q>-<year>.md)

Files here bypass the publishing voice + cite gates (intel/ is internal).
